  "summary": "Malicious code in mnemoniclib (PyPI)",
  "details": "Clone of a legitimate library with added malicious code that runs during generating a new mnemonic. The malicious code collects data related to cryptocurrency wallets and selected other files, and exfiltrate them to a hardcoded location.\n\n\n---\n\nCategory: MALICIOUS - The campaign has clearly malicious intent, like infostealers.\n\n\nCampaign: 2026-03-mnemoniclib\n\n\nReasons (based on the campaign):\n\n\n - clones-real-package\n\n\n - action-hidden-in-lib-usage\n\n\n - crypto-related\n\n\n - exfiltration-crypto\n\n\n - files-exfiltration\n\n",
